data.description: Upon walking in you will notice the beautiful workmanship of this magnificent home.   Featuring charms of yesteryear but with the conveniences of today.  Quality from the past with beautiful woodwork, a parlor, vestibule and the one of a kind feeling this home offers.  Several pocket doors on the main level bring you privacy with style.  The room sizes are fantastic, and the kitchen is a dream come true.  Cabinets galore in this custom kitchen, granite countertops, sliding pull outs, special lighting, a cookbook area and the list goes on.  We have you covered with a newer roof which was installed in the summer of 2021. Do you need 2 bathrooms?  Well, we have the space to make your dream come true.    The garage features a furnace, loft with loads of storage and an automatic garage door opener.  A new Central air unit was installed this year.  If you are cramped or need space no need to worry.  There is a lot of storage space and closets.  The walk up attic is fantastic and ready for additional room.  Completely floored and boasting electric and windows.  Square foot of the home is an estimate.
